---
import Container from "./Container.astro"
---
<Container>
<div class="relative flex flex-col-reverse items-center md:flex-row" id="hero">
    <div class="row items-center py-5 md:w-6/12 md:pb-20 md:pt-10">
        <div class="text-left space-y-3">
            <h1 class="text-5xl font-medium leading-none md:text-6xl text-center md:text-left">
                Propulsez Votre Entreprise <br/>
                <span class="text-gradient">avec des Solutions</span> <br/>
                Marketing Innovantes
            </h1>
            <p class="mt-6 mb-8 text-xl font-normal leading-7 sm:mb-12 text-center md:text-left">Experts en marketing digital, acquisition de clients et stratégies de croissance. Nos campagnes marketing personnalisées et nos tactiques innovantes aident les entreprises à se développer rapidement et à obtenir des résultats remarquables.</p>
            <div class="w-full justify-center md:justify-start items-center inline-flex">
                <a href="https://calendly.com/achraf-xchahid/30min" target="_blank" class="group px-8 py-5 bg-zinc-900 hover:bg-white rounded-2xl text-center text-white hover:text-black border text-xl font-normal leading-7 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 inline-flex items-center gap-2">
                    Réservez une consultation
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:translate-x-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
                    </svg>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex items-center py-5 md:w-6/12 md:pb-20 md:pt-10">
        <img src="/sos.gif" width="100%" alt="Hero" class="rounded-3xl shadow-2xl"/>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="flex-row items-center mt-16">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-3 sm:grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-6 gap-8">
        <div class="p-4 grayscale transition duration-200 hover:grayscale-0 hover:scale-110">
            <img src="https://www.xn--cafkhatra-d4a.com/assets/favicon-36e5bf54.svg" class="h-12 w-auto mx-auto" loading="lazy" alt="client logo" width="" height="" />
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 grayscale transition duration-200 hover:grayscale-0 hover:scale-110">
            <img src="/clients/Group 8.svg" class="h-12 w-auto mx-auto" loading="lazy" alt="client logo" width="" height="" />
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 flex grayscale transition duration-200 hover:grayscale-0 hover:scale-110">
            <img src="/clients/03.svg" class="h-9 w-auto m-auto" loading="lazy" alt="client logo" width="" height="" />
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 grayscale transition duration-200 hover:grayscale-0 hover:scale-110">
            <img src="/clients/meta.svg" class="h-10 w-auto mx-auto" loading="lazy" alt="client logo" width="" height="" />
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 flex grayscale transition duration-200 hover:grayscale-0 hover:scale-110">
            <img src="https://www.marocimpact.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/MAROC-IMPACT-BLACK-V3-01-2048x1352.png" class="h-14 w-auto m-auto" loading="lazy" alt="client logo" width="" height="" />
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 grayscale transition duration-200 hover:grayscale-0 hover:scale-110">
            <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e7/Shopify_logo.svg/2560px-Shopify_logo.svg.png" 
                class="h-12 w-auto mx-auto" 
                loading="lazy" 
                alt="Shopify logo" />
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</Container>

<style>
    .text-gradient {
        background: linear-gradient(to right, theme(colors.zime.44), #4ADE80);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
    }

    .client-logo {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(20px);
    }

    .client-logo.visible {
        animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease forwards;
    }

    @keyframes fadeInUp {
        from {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(20px);
        }
        to {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
    }
</style>